<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨٢٩ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَحَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/893">‌بُدَيْلٌ </a>، أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1448">‌الْحَسَنَ بْنَ مُسْلِمٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَمْ أَرَهُمْ يَرَوْنَ بِالصَّبِرِ بَأْسًا»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>